OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FTraders who attended this year's Royal
OL,8,FCornwall Show have said they have lost
OL,9,Fthousands of pounds because the last
OL,10,Fday was cancelled.
OL,12,FShow organisers made the decision not
OL,13,Fto open on Saturday, usually the
OL,14,Fbusiest day, after the Met Office
OL,15,Fissued a yellow weather warning and
OL,16,Fsaid winds could reach up to 50 miles
OL,17,Fan hour.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FAlthough the traders understood the
OL,8,Freasons behind the decision, many were
OL,9,Fsmall businesses who had invested
OL,10,Fheavily in stock, in some cases
OL,11,Fperishable items such as food and
OL,12,Fflowers.
OL,14,FHowever in a true community spirit
OL,15,Fpeople rallied round and some
OL,16,Fbusinesses managed to sell some of
OL,17,Ftheir stock from home, with people
OL,18,Fforming queues to support the traders.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FBruno Vicende and Athina Selina, Co-
OL,8,Fowners The Magic Whisk in St Austell
OL,9,Fhad started their day at 2am on
OL,10,FSaturday preparing and packing their
OL,11,Fcakes for the show.
OL,13,FOn Saturday afternoon they were forced
OL,14,Fto sell the cakes from their front
OL,15,Flawn. People came from Falmouth, Truro
OL,16,Fand Newquay.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FAthina said: "We had stock that was
OL,8,Fworth over #2,000. Obviously that's
OL,9,Fnot the cost of your ingredients but
OL,10,Fthat's everything. The pitch for the
OL,11,Fshow and staff and everything. But we
OL,12,Fjust thought, oh, we'll just lose
OL,13,Feverything. We would obviously give it
OL,14,Fto people.
OL,16,F"But you know, you wait, you've worked
OL,17,Fso hard when you have an artisan
OL,18,Fproduct, it's endless sleepless
OL,19,Fnights, stress, trying to get
OL,20,Feverything ready.
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,F"We never imagined anything even
OL,8,Fremotely close to what happened. Lucy
OL,9,FBakes had the same outcome until she
OL,10,Fsold out. So the support from the
OL,11,Fpeople was incredible.
OL,13,F"I feel like everyone needed that
OL,14,Fhope. Like the world is quite dark at
OL,15,Fthe moment, so I think everyone just
OL,16,Fsort of came out in support and it was
OL,17,Fincredible."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
