OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FIt's the first time since 1993 that
OL,8,Fthe show has been cancelled because of
OL,9,Fthe weather. Mark Stoddard, Secretary,
OL,10,FRoyal Cornwall Agricultural
OL,11,FAssociation said it was a very
OL,12,Fdifficult decision to make.
OL,14,FHe said: "The Royal Cornwall Show
OL,15,Ffamily has so many different aspects
OL,16,Fand I was going to let them down.
OL,26,@vD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,F"It was the right decision, we have no
OL,8,Fchoice, the weather conditions we had
OL,9,Fseen in the middle of the night had
OL,10,Fbattered the showground, portaloos had
OL,11,Fblown over, a lot of the gazebos had
OL,12,Fgone.
OL,14,FMr Stoddard said they have yet to make
OL,15,Fa final decision about refunds adding:
OL,16,F"We are a charity and we have to talk
OL,17,Fto the board and make those decisions
OL,18,Fbut in reality the public tickets will
OL,19,Fbe refunded, that's the most
OL,20,Fstraightforward.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,F"There are about 30,000 so this is not
OL,8,Fgoing to be a quick and easy process,
OL,9,Fit's going to take quite a while to co-
OL,10,Fordinate and organise those repayments.
OL,12,F"The stallholders are the hardest one
OL,13,Fbecause they did have two days
OL,14,Ftrading, but for some trade stands
OL,15,FSaturday is their key day, while for
OL,16,Fothers the Saturday is virtually
OL,17,Firrelevant to them, so that's going to
OL,18,Fbe a much harder decision as to how we
OL,19,Fdo that."
OL,26,@tD@AOU{D@IO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FAt Treway Farm near Grampound, St
OL,8,FAustell, Kate Martin has begun the
OL,9,Fprocess of freezing what she can.
OL,11,FShe managed to sell some of her meat
OL,12,Fproducts at a farm shop on Sunday, but
OL,13,Fstill has half of it leftover.
OL,15,FMs Martin said: "Across the burgers
OL,16,Fand the fresh meat we've lost ten to
OL,17,F15 thousand pounds.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,F"So now we won't make any money from
OL,8,Fthe show. We're now just in damage
OL,9,Flimitation territory, which is huge
OL,10,Ffor our small business.
OL,12,F"The show is a massive part of our
OL,13,Fyear and is a massive mid-year boost
OL,14,Fbefore we move into Christmas, and the
OL,15,Fsame for lots and lots of other
OL,16,Ftraders. The show is the big thing."
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUxD@dO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FMs Martin said that they normally call
OL,8,Fthe Saturday show day "Super Saturday"
OL,9,Fbecause of its importance to their
OL,10,Fbusiness, normally it's the only day
OL,11,Fthey make a profit.
OL,13,FKate added: "We did a sale at the farm
OL,14,Fyesterday, and we were absolutely
OL,15,Fblown away by the number of people who
OL,16,Fcame. It's that real sense of
OL,17,Fcommunity in Cornwall where when the
OL,18,Fchips are down, people do come out and
OL,19,Fdo support you.
OL,26,@pD@WOUpD@fO]uD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43412
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,F"We did a 10% discount. And we had so
OL,8,Fmany customers who were like, no, no,
OL,9,Fno, we want to pay full price for it.
OL,10,FIt was a really sort of life affirming
OL,11,Fafternoon."
OL,13,FA number of local farmers markets and
OL,14,Fother venues, including the Eden
OL,15,FProject, offered the traders pitches
OL,16,Fto sell off at least some of their
OL,17,Fstock.
OL,26,@sD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
