OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43413
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1781010670
OL,3,CTicket for Saturday's Royal Cornwall
OL,4,Cto be refunded as traders count the
OL,5,Ccost
OL,7,FAndy Jasper, CEO at The Eden Project
OL,8,Fsaid: "Cornwall is a thriving
OL,9,Fecosystem of interconnected local
OL,10,Fbusinesses, and many of these traders
OL,11,Fare our suppliers, we couldn't offer
OL,12,Fthe experiences we do without them.
OL,14,F"Supporting local communities is a
OL,15,Fpart of Eden's DNA and typical of how
OL,16,Fwe do things in Cornwall, so stepping
OL,17,Fin to help out, especially during our
OL,18,FBig Lunch and Big Help Out weekend,
OL,19,Fwhich is all about food and community,
OL,20,Fwas simply the right thing to do."
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
